                <h4 class="mb-0">Share & Earn with Glowly</h4>
                <p>Refer your friends and earn ₹100 on their first purchase!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stats-container mb-4">
                <div class="stat-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-gift achievement-icon"></i>
